---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Projects – Raúl Abad" lang="en">
  <div class="container mx-auto p-8 space-y-16">
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-sky-300">
        Selected work
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white">
        Projects I’ve contributed to
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-slate-200/90 max-w-3xl">
        I combine experience in <span class="font-semibold">digital products</span> and
        <span class="font-semibold">European public sector projects</span>, working on
        frontend, backend, APIs and architecture.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-sky-200">
        NeuronUP · Neurorehabilitation platform
      </h3>
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.3fr)_minmax(0,1fr)] gap-10 items-start"
      >
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-200/90">
            Development and maintenance of the <span class="font-semibold">NeuronUP</span>
            product using <span class="font-semibold">Symfony</span> and
            <span class="font-semibold">Angular</span>. Design and implementation of REST
            APIs, integration with other services and creation of custom console
            commands to support admin users in their daily operations.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-slate-300/90">
            The focus is on delivering a robust, secure and easy‑to‑evolve
            platform, improving usability and performance in each iteration.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2">
            <span
              class="rounded-full bg-slate-800/70 border border-sky-500/40 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-sky-200"
              >Symfony</span
            >
            <span
              class="rounded-full bg-slate-800/70 border border-emerald-500/40 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-200"
              >Angular</span
            >
            <span
              class="rounded-full bg-slate-800/70 border border-indigo-500/40 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-indigo-200"
              >REST APIs</span
            >
            <span
              class="rounded-full bg-slate-800/70 border border-slate-500/40 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-slate-200"
              >Full‑Stack</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-700/70 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900/80 to-slate-950/80 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-sky-900/40"
        >
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-sky-200 tracking-wide mb-3">
            Role
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-slate-100 mb-4">
            Full‑Stack Developer, responsible for new features, corrective and
            evolutive maintenance and technical integrations.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
            <span class="font-medium text-slate-200">Period</span> · June 2024 –
            Present
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://neuronup.com/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-sky-300 hover:text-sky-200"
          >
            Visit product
            <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-sky-200">
        UNDRR, ENC, ESMA, ERC · European Union projects
      </h3>
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.3fr)_minmax(0,1fr)] gap-10 items-start"
      >
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-200/90">
            Backend development with <span class="font-semibold">Drupal</span> and
            <span class="font-semibold">PHP</span> for international projects such as
            <span class="font-semibold">UNDRR</span>,
            <span class="font-semibold">ENC</span>,
            <span class="font-semibold">ESMA</span> and
            <span class="font-semibold">ERC</span>. Custom module development, API
            creation and full site building to deliver stable and maintainable
            platforms.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-slate-300/90">
            Work based on agile methodologies (SCRUM), using
            <span class="font-semibold">GitHub</span> for version control and
            <span class="font-semibold">Docker</span> for Linux‑based environment
            setup.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2">
            <span
              class="rounded-full bg-slate-800/70 border border-sky-500/40 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-sky-200"
              >Drupal 7/8/9</span
            >
            <span
              class="rounded-full bg-slate-800/70 border border-amber-500/40 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-amber-200"
              >PHP 7.4 / 8.1</span
            >
            <span
              class="rounded-full bg-slate-800/70 border border-indigo-500/40 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-indigo-200"
              >Symfony</span
            >
            <span
              class="rounded-full bg-slate-800/70 border border-slate-500/40 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-slate-200"
              >Docker · GitHub · SCRUM</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-700/70 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900/80 to-slate-950/80 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-sky-900/40 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-100"
        >
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-sky-200 mb-1">Highlighted projects</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-slate-200/90">
              <li>UNDRR · Content platform for disaster risk reduction</li>
              <li>ENC · Portal for the European Commission</li>
              <li>ESMA · European Securities and Markets Authority</li>
              <li>ERC · European Research Council</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-400">
            <span class="font-medium text-slate-200">Role</span> · Drupal Backend
            Developer at NTT DATA.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</Layout>


